PP%2Fsummer98%2Fquckened_conscience.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVoluntarism+%28action%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20071213221221/http://www.lermuseum.org/ler/mh/wwii/voluntarism.html\">\"Military History: Second World War: Homefront, 1940\u201345\"</a>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lermuseum.org/ler/mh/wwii/voluntarism.html\">the original</a> on December 13, 2007<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">December 23,</span> 2007</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Military+History%3A+Second+World+War%3A+Homefront%2C+1940%E2%80%9345&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lermuseum.org%2Fler%2Fmh%2Fwwii%2Fvoluntarism.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVoluntarism+%28action%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span>; <cite class=\"citation book\">John O'Sullivan (1982). <i>From Voluntarism to Conscription: Congress and Selective Service, 1940\u20131945</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=From+Voluntarism+to+Conscription%3A+Congress+and+Selective+Service%2C+1940%E2%80%931945&amp;rft.date=1982&amp;rft.au=John+O%27Sullivan&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVoluntarism+%28action%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span>; <cite class=\"citation web\">Christopher Jehn; Zachary Selden (2002). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.rand.org/pubs/monographs/MG265/images/webS0228.pdf\">\"The End of Conscripti